Title: Eleven Angry Jurors
Plot: The lone holdout member of a jury is found dead in the jury room. Nick reopens a four-year-old case when the sister of the victim comes forward with new evidence.
GuestStars: Ever Carradine, Eddie Jemison, Billy Wirth, Dean Norris, Jack Laufer, Susan May Pratt, Andy Berman, Chelsea Bond, Andy Powers, Sarah Rafferty, Sarah Buxton, Anne Betancourt, Darryl Alan Reed
